{"tid":41719,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（無圖）屋企人煮飯好難食 點算？","createTime":"2016-12-16T05:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T06:58:29.000Z","uid":27200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c12b1bae5f8155526827b21377d5fd23c5be7d91","tid":41719,"uid":27200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:59:43.000Z","msg":"由細食到大 我屋企都堅持唔出街食<br />\n實行健康人生<br />\n奈何屋企人一向煮飯都難食<br />\n有次旁觀佢煮飯 我問佢鼓油鹽要落幾多<br />\n佢答我睇心情 從來唔會計個個份量要落幾茶匙<br />\n隨便shoot d調味料落去就算 我調！<br />\n個餸次次出黎都咸過死海d鹽<br />\n呢樣我都算 仲有飯可以送 溝稀d味<br />\n但近排屋企人話要試新菜式<br />\n我心入面打左個突<br />\n心諗：點都好味過幽默大師2014掛<br />\n點知出到黎係 黃瓜攪午肉碎配沙律醬 <br />\n你無睇錯阿！係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沙律醬</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/133523_c4915519366017f480a956f2e77a987e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F133523_c4915519366017f480a956f2e77a987e.jpg&h=d317df23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個時候佢笑住口問：好唔好味阿？<br />\n我問佢：做咩咁凍既？<br />\n佢話：沙律醬放係雪櫃凍架嘛！<br />\n我：。。。。。。<br />\n佢夾左幾條黃瓜試下<br />\n點哂頭咁話：幾好味 不過好似唔夠咸<br />\n心諗：（放得沙律醬仲想點咸法？）。。。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個時候佢坐係電視前面 準備睇都市閒情既《上門教煮餸》<br />\n而我只好頭也不回地低頭食屎<br />\nTVB：......想煮呢道菜式？可以留意番tvb網站既食譜<br />\n而我就慢慢咁步入房間 準備接受今晚第二輪既洗禮"},{"pid":"bf040c1c02634e684c54ed47cd842984ef01d360","tid":41719,"uid":35875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:04:24.000Z","msg":"你煮返比屋企人食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24bd6869e2560e41fff03128181189ba255a0ccf","tid":41719,"uid":50358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:06:55.000Z","msg":"會唔會其實屎仲好食"},{"pid":"c3b7e9fa78f6313594b47458703413bc888cbc02","tid":41719,"uid":62006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:15:33.000Z","msg":"你做煮嗰個囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6943f2b568a601174878f47f289f6b7363ab0be","tid":41719,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:16:32.000Z","msg":"你認真少少同佢講，好撚難食<br />\n我曾幾何時都係咁，直至我同我老母講，你抄啲菜我要過三次熱水先食得落<br />\n之後個調味終於好反少少<br />\n如果伯母過60，會唔會味蕾退化？"},{"pid":"ba2c185b9200503422c16f26de3a1ae71751feab","tid":41719,"uid":27200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:24:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你認真少少同佢講，好撚難食<br />\n我曾幾何時都係咁，直至我同我老母講，你抄啲菜我要過三次熱水先食得落<br />\n之後個調味終於好反少少<br />\n如果伯母過60，會唔會味蕾退化？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n70都黎緊<br />\n講過幾次 都係無變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e5172433ed06805ede228f355d52491dd7148f","tid":41719,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:26:58.000Z","msg":"邊撚度健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢講遲早食到腎病"},{"pid":"a7605a6997f097256c44c6091834e8e9f9ea0e43","tid":41719,"uid":54744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:52:49.000Z","msg":"最大問題係話佐唔聽既老母<br />\n冇心機，好多簡單菜色都唔識❪蕃茄炒蛋都唔識呀❫<br />\n但佢仲要堅持煮飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又難食又食黎食去得兩三樣"},{"pid":"1557eb26c3d17801da707e1ff1f1d8234974bc3a","tid":41719,"uid":8745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:55:09.000Z","msg":"蝦醬煮西瓜皮<br />\n哈密瓜皮滾瘦肉湯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599237c47140604cd9cff1fd4477f641bce06e10","tid":41719,"uid":17849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"你煮 有人煮俾你食仲想點"},{"pid":"a87e33296fa0b929eb40f0092f47356f333022f0","tid":41719,"uid":8745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蝦醬煮西瓜皮<br />\n哈<span style=\"color: red;\">蜜</span>瓜皮滾瘦肉湯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkg